PLA_CMN_20080731.0044	0	900.0	1000.0	speaker	unknown	unknown	"Processes to organize and implement the contingency measures have been clearly defined," explained the person responsible of the Environmental Protection Department. During the Olympic Games, if adversely affected by extreme weather conditions, and it is forecast that the air quality standard in the next 48 hours would exceed the standard, the operating commanding department will put forward suggestions to initiate contingency measures and report to the command headquarters. When the measures are approved, they will be organized and implemented by Beijing Municipality, Tianjin Municipality, and Hebei Province governments. The Environmental Protection Department is responsible for coordination and supervision.	0	0	0		
